Troll Hunter



Trolls aren't quite as badass as their Orc counterparts, but that might be attributed to their preference for warmer climates. Sometimes, it's just too hot to destroy everything. Nonetheless - a pissed-off troll is not a pleasant thing to encounter... As a troll, you might want to watch your tempter, lest you wind up in a bad, bad place because of it.

As a hunter, you prefer to be on the sidelines. You would rather see all angles of a situation - probably to find the best position to shoot from. You like animals, but mostly because they (might) do your bidding.
